className.description: Class names applied to the element or a function that returns them based on the component's state.

errors.description: Controlled error messages, usually from server-side validation.

nativeValidate.description: If true, the form will use native HTML validation, showing browser-native popup messages.

onClearErrors.description: Callback fired when controlled messages should be cleared.

render.description: A function to customize rendering of the component.
